parameters.name: BS2E RATE1
parameters.description: Column contains average BS2E particle flux with guard counters placed in anticoincidence with primary detectors to reduce the background from high-energy particles penetrating through the sides of the telescope.

parameters.name: Standard Deviation in BS2E RATE1
parameters.description: Column contains the statistical error associated with the BS2E RATE with guard counters in anticoincidence with primary detectors.

parameters.name: BS2E RATE2
parameters.description: Column contains average BS2E particle flux with guard counters turned off.

parameters.name: Standard Deviation in BS2E RATE2
parameters.description: Column contains the statistical error associated with the BS2E RATE with guard counters turned off.
